39
00:03:42.806 --> 00:03:44.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But Kaede
needs me!

40
00:03:47.394 --> 00:03:48.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

41
00:03:52.482 --> 00:03:53.900 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Watch out!

42
