they could harm any human.

55
00:04:51.750 --> 00:04:53.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hm. Huh?

56
00:04:54.044 --> 00:04:57.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
