master password to reboot it. Understand--

59
00:05:05.764 --> 00:05:07.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not a word. No.

60
00:05:12.020 --> 00:05:14.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
