I just don't know...

64
00:05:30.273 --> 00:05:31.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What the hell do you
think you're doing?

65
00:05:32.207 --> 00:05:34.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Do you plan on defending
that murderer?

66
00:05:34.668 --> 00:05:39.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
