Nor do I follow your code of justice.

67
00:05:39.464 --> 00:05:42.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I obey the voice
of Thanatos.

68
00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:48.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'll uncover your true identity.
And the mastermind behind this chaos.

69
00:05:48.690 --> 00:05:49.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

70
00:06:09.536 --> 00:06:11.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
