their very best to defend Stern Bild.

83
00:06:46.781 --> 00:06:49.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Gentlemen, we must have faith in
our heroes

84
00:06:49.618 --> 00:06:52.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
