87
00:07:10.988 --> 00:07:11.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dammit!

88
00:07:13.141 --> 00:07:15.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
