our powers recharge!

89
00:07:15.644 --> 00:07:18.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If they can't beat that thing,
then who can?

90
00:07:26.029 --> 00:07:28.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
