107
00:08:13.576 --> 00:08:15.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes, let it sink in...

108
00:08:22.085 --> 00:08:24.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
