127
00:09:24.240 --> 00:09:25.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Augh!

128
00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:26.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
