129
00:09:28.443 --> 00:09:29.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Agh!

130
00:09:44.084 --> 00:09:48.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
