Kotetsu!

145
00:10:55.822 --> 00:10:58.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Everything is going
according to plan.

146
00:10:59.742 --> 00:11:01.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>It appears you have</i>
<i>things under control</i>.

147
00:11:02.036 --> 00:11:04.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I do. Even with their powers activated,

148
00:11:04.998 --> 00:11:08.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
H-01's speed and strength
are on a whole different level.

149
00:11:08.418 --> 00:11:11.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Which means it's time to rid the world of
these miserable NEXT.

150
00:11:11.629 --> 00:11:14.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yes, I've just finished
making the arrangements.

151
00:11:14.549 --> 00:11:18.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When we're finished, it'll look like they
all died honorably in the line of duty.

152
00:11:34.819 --> 00:11:38.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You can keep attacking all you'd like,
but it won't make a scratch on him.

153
00:11:43.995 --> 00:11:44.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Now!

154
00:11:44.996 --> 00:11:46.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm on it, partner!

155
00:11:46.623 --> 00:11:48.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[suit]
<i>Good Luck Mode!</i>

156
00:11:49.334 --> 00:11:50.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[suit]
<i>Good Luck Mode!</i>

157
00:11:56.341 --> 00:11:58.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

158
00:11:59.093 --> 00:12:01.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[suit]
<i>Three... Two... One...</i>

159
00:12:02.305 --> 00:12:04.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[suit] <i>Tiger &amp; Bunny.</i>
<i>Over and Out!</i>

160
00:12:13.775 --> 00:12:15.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We did it!

161
00:12:16.027 --> 00:12:17.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

162
00:12:18.905 --> 00:12:19.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No way...

163
00:12:28.373 --> 00:12:29.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

164
00:12:33.503 --> 00:12:34.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunts]

165
00:12:35.637 --> 00:12:37.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting continues]

166
00:12:40.510 --> 00:12:41.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bunny!

167
00:12:48.977 --> 00:12:52.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Wild Tiger groaning]

168
00:13:07.620 --> 00:13:08.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No more...

169
00:13:09.580 --> 00:13:11.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Why don't you
just go down,

170
00:13:11.666 --> 00:13:13.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
you bastard!

171
00:13:20.925 --> 00:13:22.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu...

172
00:13:24.178 --> 00:13:25.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Barnaby] We're not giving up...

173
00:13:26.014 --> 00:13:27.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and we're not
backing down.

174
00:13:28.474 --> 00:13:29.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tiger] Ya hear that, tin man?

175
00:13:30.101 --> 00:13:32.186 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's gonna be a fight
to the finish!

176
00:13:35.315 --> 00:13:36.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[both grunting]

177
00:13:54.292 --> 00:13:57.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[both groaning painfully]

178
00:14:05.803 --> 00:14:06.763 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I've decided.

179
00:14:07.638 --> 00:14:10.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What an unfortunate turn
of events for you heroes.

180
00:14:10.850 --> 00:14:13.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It seems Blue Rose
has made up her mind!

181
00:14:13.728 --> 00:14:15.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

182
00:14:15.772 --> 00:14:19.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Go ahead, Blue Rose.
Reach up and push the button.

183
00:14:24.697 --> 00:14:26.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I refuse to push it.

184
00:14:26.616 --> 00:14:27.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

185
00:14:28.743 --> 00:14:30.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I decided that I
believe in my friends.

186
00:14:32.997 --> 00:14:36.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Tiger and Barnaby?
I believe in them too!

187
00:14:36.292 --> 00:14:39.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Are you telling me that
was your big revelation!?

188
00:14:40.296 --> 00:14:43.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Listen guys! We have to
believe they can win this.

189
00:14:46.969 --> 00:14:48.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We know how strong they can be.

190
00:14:49.263 --> 00:14:51.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So we have to be
just as strong!

191
00:14:53.893 --> 00:14:57.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're all my friends, and I'd
trust any of you with my life.

192
00:14:57.438 --> 00:14:58.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's being a hero.

193
00:15:00.191 --> 00:15:02.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I believe in Tiger
and Barnaby too.

194
00:15:02.610 --> 00:15:05.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They can win this.
I know they can win this!

195
00:15:06.656 --> 00:15:07.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Damn straight.

196
00:15:08.825 --> 00:15:12.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
If a hero can't believe in his friends...
then what good is he?

197
00:15:12.787 --> 00:15:13.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, that's right.

198
00:15:14.038 --> 00:15:17.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And yet, I...
I doubted them...

199
00:15:17.500 --> 00:15:21.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Thank you, Blue Rose.
And thanks again all of you!

200
00:15:23.756 --> 00:15:25.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Are you done yet?

201
00:15:25.383 --> 00:15:28.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
All this "trust" and "friendship" garbage
is making me sick!

202
00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:30.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[chuckles]

203
00:15:31.013 --> 00:15:32.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Go on, H-01!

204
00:15:33.015 --> 00:15:35.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Slice that pair of
idiots into pieces!

205
00:15:59.417 --> 00:16:01.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dammit... Nothing works.

206
00:16:07.258 --> 00:16:08.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[grunting]

207
00:16:20.164 --> 00:16:21.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu?

208
00:16:21.606 --> 00:16:24.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Now, Bunny! Take this guy
out with his own gun!

209
00:16:24.817 --> 00:16:25.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What?

210
00:16:28.279 --> 00:16:29.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What about you?

211
00:16:29.822 --> 00:16:33.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don't worry about me!
I'll dodge the blast before it hits.

212
00:16:33.493 --> 00:16:34.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But how?

213
00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:35.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Just do it! Hurry!

214
00:16:41.626 --> 00:16:43.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I ain't got all day here!

215
00:16:47.340 --> 00:16:48.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Shoot him, Bunny!

216
00:16:53.346 --> 00:16:56.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[screaming]

217
00:17:08.861 --> 00:17:11.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[panting]

218
00:17:28.714 --> 00:17:30.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

219
00:17:34.512 --> 00:17:36.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-They did it!
-Fabulous!

220
00:17:41.686 --> 00:17:45.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Impossible! How could my
H-01 lose to a NEXT?

221
00:17:55.491 --> 00:17:59.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
They'll all pay.
I'll kill every one of those freaks!

222
00:18:02.665 --> 00:18:03.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasps]

223
00:18:13.718 --> 00:18:15.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Little girl?

224
00:18:18.848 --> 00:18:21.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm no little girl, I'm the
daughter of Wild Tiger!

225
00:18:24.604 --> 00:18:25.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Stay away!

226
00:18:26.063 --> 00:18:26.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[groans]

227
00:18:29.734 --> 00:18:30.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's my power!

228
00:18:31.444 --> 00:18:33.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[pained grunts]

229
00:18:40.244 --> 00:18:41.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Oh snap!

230
00:18:42.955 --> 00:18:44.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Thanks, Kaede
sweetie!

231
00:18:53.591 --> 00:18:55.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[grunts]
Fire!

232
00:19:00.931 --> 00:19:02.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah!

233
00:19:18.032 --> 00:19:19.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let's go!

234
00:19:22.662 --> 00:19:24.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Hey, we did it.
It worked!

235
00:19:25.873 --> 00:19:26.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu?

236
00:19:30.836 --> 00:19:32.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[gasp] Are you okay?

237
00:19:44.308 --> 00:19:46.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sorry, bud.
I just wasn't fast enough.

238
00:19:47.978 --> 00:19:49.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Shoot him, Bunny!

239
00:19:52.233 --> 00:19:56.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Kotetsu] <i>Guess it's hard to dodge like</i>
<i>that without any power left.</i>

240
00:19:58.489 --> 00:20:02.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Heh. And it had to happen
during our final attack together.

241
00:20:02.410 --> 00:20:05.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What're you saying? Why
would your powers run out?

242
00:20:05.830 --> 00:20:07.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You still had
plenty of time!

243
00:20:08.499 --> 00:20:13.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
To be honest, my power can
barely last four lousy minutes.

244
00:20:13.504 --> 00:20:14.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Huh?

245
00:20:14.463 --> 00:20:15.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
See it's been
getting weaker...

246
00:20:16.257 --> 00:20:18.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Weaker? For how long!?

247
00:20:18.426 --> 00:20:21.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's been fadin' for
a couple months.

248
00:20:22.146 --> 00:20:24.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It was pretty tough tryin'
to keep it from you, pal.

249
00:20:24.515 --> 00:20:26.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Don't you think I
should've known!?

250
00:20:26.350 --> 00:20:28.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Why did you keep it
a secret from me!?

251
00:20:28.394 --> 00:20:31.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, because I knew you'd worry about me.
Didn't want that.

252
00:20:31.689 --> 00:20:33.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Wait, is that why you were quitting?

253
00:20:33.941 --> 00:20:36.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So you're going to quit being a hero,
just like that?

254
00:20:36.652 --> 00:20:38.612 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Being a hero is
unpredictable.

255
00:20:38.738 --> 00:20:42.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's fine when you're a young man,
but I'm gettin' too old for this stuff.

256
00:20:44.744 --> 00:20:48.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm so sorry. You were in
bad shape this whole time...

257
00:20:48.664 --> 00:20:50.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and I didn't see it.

258
00:20:51.500 --> 00:20:54.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You dummy. That was the whole point
of hiding it from you.

259
00:20:54.670 --> 00:20:56.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So you wouldn't see.

260
00:20:56.839 --> 00:20:58.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[coughs]

261
00:21:00.676 --> 00:21:03.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Listen, I... I don't
think I'm gonna make it.

262
00:21:03.596 --> 00:21:05.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Stop talking,
just lay still.

263
00:21:05.556 --> 00:21:06.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But, Bunny...

264
00:21:07.141 --> 00:21:08.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I said stop it!

265
00:21:08.726 --> 00:21:13.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Chasing after the bad guys with you,
and listening to your lame lectures...

266
00:21:13.147 --> 00:21:14.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I loved every minute of it.

267
00:21:15.024 --> 00:21:17.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
The truth is, when you finally
started calling me "Kotetsu,"

268
00:21:18.277 --> 00:21:21.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
you made me so happy I went out
on an all-night bender to celebrate.

269
00:21:22.156 --> 00:21:24.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
This isn't the end.
Stop talking like that!

270
00:21:24.784 --> 00:21:26.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Thanks for
everything, buddy.

271
00:21:26.911 --> 00:21:30.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Shut up, Kotetsu!
You're not dying, you hear me?

272
00:21:30.539 --> 00:21:32.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're not the kind of
person who gives up!

273
00:21:33.083 --> 00:21:34.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're optimistic,
dammit, act it!

274
00:21:35.085 --> 00:21:39.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Besides, I've been learning to make
fried rice and that's your favorite dish!

275
00:21:39.215 --> 00:21:41.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So you have to live
so you can try it!

276
00:21:43.177 --> 00:21:44.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No!

277
00:21:44.970 --> 00:21:46.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whoa, so close...

278
00:21:47.181 --> 00:21:50.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Ya know, you've got really
long eyelashes...

279
00:21:52.895 --> 00:21:54.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu...?

280
00:21:55.606 --> 00:21:57.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kotetsu!

